---
import "../../styles/theme.css";
import "../../styles/landing.css";
import LandingHeader from "../../components/landing-header.astro";
import LandingFooter from "../../components/landing-footer.astro";

const canonicalURL = "https://freellms.vercel.app/alternatives/openai/";
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" data-theme="dark">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="canonical" href={canonicalURL} />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Geist:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Geist+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <title>FreeLLM vs OpenAI API: Get GPT-quality models at zero cost</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="FreeLLM is a free, self-hosted OpenAI-compatible gateway with 32+ models. Compare it to the OpenAI API and decide which fits your use case."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="FreeLLM vs OpenAI API: Get GPT-quality models at zero cost" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="FreeLLM routes to free-tier providers including GitHub Models, Groq, and Gemini. Same OpenAI SDK. Zero cost."
    />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/og-image.png" />
    <meta property="og:url" content={canonicalURL} />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/og-image.png" />

  </head>
  <body>
    <LandingHeader />
    <main>
      <article class="alt-page">
        <span class="page-eyebrow">comparison</span>
        <h1>FreeLLM vs OpenAI API</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          OpenAI's API is great, but every token costs money. FreeLLM routes to free-tier providers
          including GitHub Models, which serves GPT-4o-mini, plus Groq, Gemini, Mistral, and five
          others. You keep the exact same OpenAI SDK. You swap one URL.
        </p>

        <h2>Side-by-side comparison</h2>

        <div class="table-shell">
          <table class="alt-table">
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Feature</th>
                <th class="freellm-col">FreeLLM</th>
                <th>OpenAI API</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>Cost</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">$0 (free tiers only)</td>
                <td>Pay per token</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Models available</td>
                <td class="freellm-col">32+ (Llama 3.3 70B, Gemini 2.5 Pro, GPT-4o-mini via GitHub Models, Mistral, Cerebras)</td>
                <td>GPT-4o, GPT-4o-mini, o1, o3 and others</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Setup time</td>
                <td class="freellm-col">~2 minutes (one-click deploy)</td>
                <td>Immediate (managed service)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Rate limits</td>
                <td class="freellm-col">~450 req/min (3 keys x 8 providers, automatic failover)</td>
                <td>Tier-based, increases with spend</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Self-hosted</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes (MIT licensed)</td>
                <td class="no">No (managed only)</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>OpenAI SDK compatible</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Automatic failover</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Yes (8 providers)</td>
                <td class="no">No</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>Dashboard</td>
                <td class="freellm-col yes">Real-time, included</td>
                <td class="yes">Yes (usage.openai.com)</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2>When to use OpenAI API instead</h2>
        <p>
          OpenAI's API makes more sense in these situations:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>You need GPT-4o full, o1, or o3 specifically. FreeLLM's free tiers do not include those models.</li>
          <li>You need a guaranteed uptime SLA. Free-tier providers do not offer one.</li>
          <li>You are running production traffic where a 429 or cold-start is not acceptable.</li>
          <li>You want a single vendor to call for support.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These are real tradeoffs. If any of them matter for your project, pay OpenAI.
        </p>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2>When FreeLLM makes sense</h2>
        <p>
          FreeLLM fits well when you are in one of these situations:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Prototyping or exploring ideas. You do not want an API bill while figuring things out.</li>
          <li>Testing prompts across multiple models. FreeLLM lets you compare Llama, Gemini, and Mistral responses without managing separate SDKs.</li>
          <li>Side projects with low or bursty traffic. The automatic failover absorbs rate limit spikes so you do not have to.</li>
          <li>You want dev costs at zero and are comfortable with best-effort reliability.</li>
        </ul>

        <hr class="divider" />

        <h2>The code change is one line</h2>
        <p>
          If you already use the OpenAI SDK, switching to FreeLLM for development is a single
          environment variable change. Your production code can keep pointing at OpenAI.
        </p>

        <div class="code-shell">
          <div class="code-label">python — before (OpenAI)</div>
          <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> <span class="token-var">openai</span> <span class="token-keyword">import</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>

<span class="token-var">client</span> = <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>(
    <span class="token-var">api_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"sk-..."</span>
)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="code-shell">
          <div class="code-label">python — after (FreeLLM)</div>
          <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">from</span> <span class="token-var">openai</span> <span class="token-keyword">import</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>

<span class="token-var">client</span> = <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>(
    <span class="token-var">base_url</span>=<span class="token-string">"https://your-freellm-instance/v1"</span>,  <span class="token-comment"># only change</span>
    <span class="token-var">api_key</span>=<span class="token-string">"your-freellm-key"</span>
)</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="code-shell">
          <div class="code-label">node.js — after (FreeLLM)</div>
          <pre><code><span class="token-keyword">import</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span> <span class="token-keyword">from</span> <span class="token-string">"openai"</span>;

<span class="token-keyword">const</span> <span class="token-var">client</span> = <span class="token-keyword">new</span> <span class="token-var">OpenAI</span>(&lbrace;
  <span class="token-var">baseURL</span>: <span class="token-string">"https://your-freellm-instance/v1"</span>,  <span class="token-comment">// only change</span>
  <span class="token-var">apiKey</span>: <span class="token-string">"your-freellm-key"</span>,
&rbrace;);</code></pre>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-block">
          <p>Deploy FreeLLM to Railway or Render in about 2 minutes. Bring your own free-tier API keys.</p>
          <a href="/quickstart/" class="btn-primary">Deploy FreeLLM in 2 minutes</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </main>
    <LandingFooter />
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  .alt-page {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 8rem;
  }

  .alt-page .page-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.375rem 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.18);
    color: hsl(158, 50%, 65%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .alt-page h1 {
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .alt-page .lead {
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    margin: 0 0 3.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }

  .alt-page h2 {
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .alt-page p {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .alt-page ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .alt-page ul li {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
  }

  .table-shell {
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .alt-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 15%);
  }

  .alt-table th {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    text-align: left;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 13%);
    color: hsl(158, 50%, 65%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
  }

  .alt-table td {
    padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.07);
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 75%);
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .alt-table tbody tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .alt-table tbody tr:hover {
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.03);
  }

  .alt-table td:first-child {
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 85%);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .alt-table .freellm-col {
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.05);
  }

  .yes {
    color: hsl(158, 50%, 60%);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
  }

  .no {
    color: hsl(0, 50%, 55%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
  }

  .partial {
    color: hsl(38, 90%, 55%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
  }

  .code-shell {
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem;
  }

  .code-label {
    padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 13%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 22%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 50%);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .code-shell pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    background: hsl(224, 14%, 15%);
    font-family: "Geist Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 88%);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .code-shell code {
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    color: inherit;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  .token-comment { color: hsl(0, 0%, 45%); }
  .token-keyword { color: hsl(200, 80%, 65%); }
  .token-string  { color: hsl(158, 50%, 60%); }
  .token-var     { color: hsl(0, 0%, 85%); }

  .cta-block {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.2);
    background: hsla(158, 50%, 40%, 0.04);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-block p {
    color: hsl(0, 0%, 65%);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .cta-block .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: hsl(158, 50%, 46%);
    color: #04140a;
    font-family: "Geist", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 280ms cubic-bezier(0.32, 0.72, 0, 1);
  }

  .cta-block .btn-primary:hover {
    background: hsl(158, 50%, 50%);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid hsl(224, 12%, 20%);
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }
</style>
